Despite what you might think based on the names, the Staceys had been around much longer than the Apostles. Their numbers were greater, their fortifications were stronger, their weapons were more powerful, and their vehicles were better maintained. The Staceys looked something like a ragtag motorcycle gang, but looks can be deceiving: they were really more akin to a well-organised militia.

